### Calendar Display
- Display tasks on calendar based on due dates
- Show recurring task instances
- Color-coded tasks by category/priority
- Visual density indicators (tasks per day)
- Multi-day task spanning visualization
- Toggle to show/hide completed tasks

### Time Management
- Time blocking: drag-and-drop tasks to schedule specific slots
- Create calendar events (meetings, appointments, deadlines)
- All-day events vs. timed events
- Event duration with start/end times
- Link tasks to calendar events for context

### Calendar Navigation
- Quick date picker/jump to date
- Today button to return to current date
- Previous/Next navigation for all views
- Mini calendar sidebar for quick month overview
- Week number display option
